oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Knoxville College Bulletin. Published Quarterly. Series 17, Number 4. June 1919. Catalogue of the Officers and Students of Knoxville College, Knoxville, Tennessee. Member of the Association of Colleges for Negro Youth. Catalogue, 1918-19. Announcements, 1919-20. Knoxville College Press 1919. The names of students and faculty are searchable.
